    - **S1 `873cfd93`**: Removed 8 cli `windows.ts` aliases + 3-line 
`V8_HEAP_MB→DEFAULT_V8_HEAP_MB` fold at `v8-profiles.ts`. Removed 
`buildConnectionString` export and `mssqlJsonExtension` adapter. Removed 
`telemetry/context/job.ts` shim.
    - **S2 `689d47b8`**: Removed `trustedConnection` option (mssql adapter). 
Removed `serveStaticFiles` and `registerFsRoutes` options (fresh package).
    - **S3a `11e946e3`**: Deleted `saga-bus-legacy.ts` + legacy saga-runtime 
branches/barrels. Removed 1 legacy-adapter test that constructed the now-deleted
`SagaBusLegacy`. Updated `docs/site/reference/sagas/index.md`. Appended 
arch-debt entry `CRON-SUBSYSTEM-DUP` (correctly scoped to 
`plugin-workers-core`+`plugin-triggers-core`).
    
