    | `deno task --cwd plugin-sagas-core test` | 28 | 28 PASS |
    | `deno task --cwd plugins/sagas test` | 37 | 37 PASS |
    | `deno task arch:check` | all | 0 FAIL (pre-existing INFO/WARN only) |
    | `deno task publish:dry-run` | all | exit 0 |
